rce-default-alias=\"f1-toy-car-banner-01.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438529\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"14\" data-media-id=\"9cf264bd-9367-402f-ba3a-e02816806269\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/f1-toy-car-banner-01.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103155098&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/f1-toy-car-banner-01.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103155098&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"k125crjcju\">Project</span></strong>:  Making a toy F1 Car</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"lj1uqksvc4\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>: Teoman Şirvancı</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"fk88khgg6u\">Edited by:</span></strong> Leif Pedersen</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/Tutorials/F1_Toy/F1_Toy_RfM.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103102010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604438529/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103102010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604438546\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438529\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"14\" data-media-id=\"0545d5ed-f58f-4b0c-ae06-06b6f4c314d7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103102010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103102010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/Tutorials/F1_Toy/F1_Backdrop_Sequence.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103102010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604438529/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103102010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604438546\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438529\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"14\" data-media-id=\"0545d5ed-f58f-4b0c-ae06-06b6f4c314d7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103102010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103102010&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-local-id=\"05ccb9a5-0334-4ce3-affc-deaaac79be9c\" data-macro-id=\"0828c9c8-0d74-4fa7-9561-0dd420dc95c8\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1084813383\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p /><p>This nostalgic F1 toy car is nearly 50 years old and belonged to my father as a child. Recreating it digitally was both a way to preserve a personal memory and an opportunity to explore different tools and workflows while creating a meaningful piece for my portfolio.</p><p>I used RenderMan for physically accurate shading and lighting. I matched the CG render with real turntable footage one-to-one, combining both through camera tracking and compositing. </p><p>This approach resulted in a presentation that blends physical nostalgia with digital visual storytelling in a single frame.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Modelling_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/Modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762532869150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604438529/Modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762532869150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"655753226\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Modelling_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438529\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"14\" data-media-id=\"ceee2824-fa52-4b43-92aa-9e25261d7d85\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/Modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762532869150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/Modelling_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762532869150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"MakingaToyF1Car-Modeling\"><span data-colorid=\"audbc3bqgt\">Modeling</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"c