2&amp;modificationDate=1758103935804&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\" /></span><p>Teoman Şirvancı is an artist specializing in hard-surface modeling and look development. He is currently building his portfolio in film and visual effects, aiming to take his first steps toward a career in the industry. Inspired by storytelling and the creative aspects of visual design, he&rsquo;s excited to grow as an artist and collaborate with creative teams.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/teovfx\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Instagram-logo.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/Instagram-logo.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103979995&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/604438529/Instagram-logo.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103979995&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"256\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"604241959\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Instagram-logo.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"604438529\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"14\" data-media-id=\"526cb32b-2eec-41df-b6c8-54a3d832d9c6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/604438529/Instagram-logo.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758103979995&amp;c